# Workspace mixes libs (tset-core, tset-py) and a binary (tset-cli) +
# benches. We follow the cargo book's recommendation: commit the
# lockfile because tset-cli is a binary product. Library consumers of
# tset-core / tset-py compute their own lockfile from their downstream
# tree — they aren't bound by ours.
!Cargo.lock

